name: MANIFESTO L'ELIXIR
description: One year after the launch of Manifesto, Saint Laurent perfumes unveil the Elixir. This more intense and vanilla release addresses a woman in search of mystery and sensuality. A woman who “feeds it the wildest dreams and exalts a plural personality.”
ingredients: ['Heliotrope', 'Jasmine (Sambac)', 'Ambroxan (Ambergris)', 'Lily Of The Valley', 'Tuberose', 'Tonka Bean', 'Vanilla', 'Bergamot', 'Cashmeran (Woody musky)', 'Cedarwood', 'Cream (Chantilly)', 'Green Notes', 'Mandarin', 'Sandalwood', 'Blackcurrant Bud']
